<item>
            <title>[LU-11095] Error: &quot; git checkout error!&quot; After pushing patch to whamcloud &amp;&amp; JIRA-Gerrit link broken</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11095</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;br/&gt;
I get Error: &quot; git checkout error!&quot; After pushing patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32724/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32724/&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32709/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32709/&lt;/a&gt; to whamcloud. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This step fails under gerrit:&lt;br/&gt;
Builder CentOS 7.2 x86_64 (TARBALL) failed (failed) - &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.lustre.org/builders/CentOS%207.2%20x86_64%20%28TARBALL%29/builds/14728&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.lustre.org/builders/CentOS%207.2%20x86_64%20%28TARBALL%29/builds/14728&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Details are:&lt;br/&gt;
git version 1.8.3.1&lt;br/&gt;
Cloning into &apos;.&apos;...&lt;br/&gt;
fatal: unable to access &apos;http://review.whamcloud.com/fs/lustre-release.git/&apos;: Failed connect to review.whamcloud.com:80; Connection timed out&lt;br/&gt;
fatal: Not a git repository (or any of the parent directories): .git&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Secondly: The JIRA-Gerrit link is broken.&lt;br/&gt;
Usually, when a patch is pushed, gerrit updates the JIRA ticket that a new patch is pushed along with the patch link. With &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11094&quot; title=&quot;Fix code style/whitespace issues&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11094&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11094&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11094&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11094&lt;/a&gt;) and its corresponding patch (&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32724/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32724/&lt;/a&gt;) this is no longer seen.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks in Advance for looking into both the issue !!!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
